name: Open Items
type: base
description: Cross-workstream view — open action items and unresolved questions. Populated from meeting notes and state MOC. Use this for at-a-glance integration state.
filters:
  - field: type
    operator: in
    values: [meeting, project, source]
view: table
columns:
  - name
  - workstream
  - last_updated
sort:
  - field: last_updated
    order: asc
notes: |
  This Base surfaces the oldest-touched items first (ascending last_updated) to highlight staleness.
  For decision-relevant open items, read the ## Open Questions section in 30 Projects/Acme-BetaCo Integration.md.
  For action item tracking, see 99 Workspace/_session_handoff.md.
